summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending plats 22E and 23W, pages 76 and 77, of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain property in the lower Wallingford Neighborhood (in Blocks 31, 32, 48, 54 through 58 inclusive, 65 and 66, Lake Union Addition, in Blocks 1 and 2 in Bagley's Addition, and in Blocks 12, 13, 16 and 17, Washington Addition) from duplex residence high density (RD 5000) zone to single family residence high density (RS 5000) zone (Petition of Wallingford Community Council, C.F. 279734, Hearing Examiner No. X-74-204).
